{"id": "art-4710", "label": "Art. 4710", "title": "Art. 4710: Utilizarea resurselor publice", "slug": "art-4710", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1624485550\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1664\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1624485550\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><u><span style='color:#569748'>Art. 47<sup>10</sup>:\nUtilizarea resurselor publice </span></u></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1453864690\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1663\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1453864690\"><![endif]></span><u><span\nstyle='color:#569748'>Persoanele prev&#259;zute la art. 47<sup>2</sup> alin.\n(1) sunt obligate s&#259; asigure:</span></u></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_626581684\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1662\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_626581684\"><![endif]></span><u><span\nstyle='color:#569748'>a)ocrotirea propriet&#259;&#355;ii publice &#351;i\nprivate a statului, folosirea util&#259; &#351;i eficient&#259; a banilor\npublici, folosirea bunurilor apar&#355;inând autorit&#259;&#355;ii sau\ninstitu&#355;iei publice numai pentru desf&#259;&#351;urarea\nactivit&#259;&#355;ilor aferente func&#355;iei de&#355;inute, în conformitate\ncu prevederile legale;</span></u></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1537774234\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1661\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1537774234\"><![endif]></span><u><span\nstyle='color:#569748'>b)tratamentul egal în ceea ce prive&#351;te participarea\npersoanelor la activit&#259;&#355;i oficiale pe care le organizeaz&#259; sau la\ncare au acces prin natura func&#355;iei exercitate în baza atribu&#355;iilor\nsau mandatului.</span></u></p>"}